NPC.Talk: Do you still remember Madame Brave mainland? Am I fascinated?
Sell excellent equipment to me to get crystal. I collect excellent equipment with powerful magic and extract the power from them to inject into other things, I only do crystal deals here.

Fight with Quinton is minions to gain experience. I follow the foot steps of my teacher, collecting miracles around the world, and guide the warriors to fight.

Because my ancestor Choban chose a wrong master, he followed Antonios who resurrected Quinton a thousand year ago. So we have to suffer the cruel consequences, and we can only wander outside.
My ancestos worked as blacksmith in the Warrior is Land, they have good talent in forging weapons and armors, the equipments made by my grandparents and I are excellent.

Emperor, immortal, conspiracy with the demon tribe. Raids of natural energy robbery Remain the villagers free. I am the strongest archer in the daemon. I am willing to join the rebel army. To show my wings 【Show wings: colorful moon Maya】

All my men died in the battle with the devil, they are all heroes. Since I was lucky to survive, I will gather more people to fight for Quinton. In order to comfort the soul of the death, I have reward for all the members of the Quinton army.

The invasion of inferno breaks the peace, and the disaster happened ten years ago is still being remembered by the people, may warriors unite against the inferno, and believe that miracle will happen again, the city will welcome tranquility again.
This is the only Town of Warrior is Land, we have to defend this place no matter what, I bleed for glory.
The creatures in Warrior is Land have rotten, we must stop this.
In order to prevent monsters from intruding the town, I can only defend here, fortunately the Warriors help to share the responsibility from time to time.
We need teens like you to cooperate with us!
May the glory of the angels, always protect you.
I use soul power eschewed by human to fight against the monster, even if I was regarded as a outlier in the human world, even if I was rejected, I do not want to see my race perished.
The triumpant emperor of PK King will take over my place.

Burdened with with heavy responsibilities, no doubt that we are the savior of this century, do not fear our power, we can bring brightness to you in the dark.

I hope the rebels will rule this area. And exorcise the kingdom with his demon tribe to hell!

Demon Gordon will die with my sword!

There are artifact fragments and powerful equipment and skills in the sea left over from civilization .
The beauty of the deep sea world has thrilled my soul.
This is the best route to the safety zone, I am here to keep an eye, I will give warning if any powerful sea monster attacks.
The first artifact fragment is in the hands of Sea Demon Sitra is, I am going to steal it.
My partner and I came here to accomplish our task,whatever it takes we will find the artifact fragments, that is the key to fight Demon King Quinton.
If the Miracle Land restores its peace, I will settle down in the deep sea, and I will be here for the rest of my life.
The helper of Demon King Quinton .. sea demon Sitra, he controls all the monsters here.

I believe, you will crush all our enemies soon.

The gravel obscured the sun, and my eyes, knowing the enemy is in front, I can only shoot the the arrows according to my feeling .

Powerful people like me and you are needed in the Sky City task

It has been years since I have been here! Now there is no glory like the past.

We are lucky to find refuge in this corner.

Can you imagine how civilized this place was?
Tool Accuracy The depth of the magic alphabet. Make me feel good!

If possible, I really don not want this place to be destroyed.
If possible, I really don not want this place to be destroyed.

Old Witch

The things unsettled today will not be settled tomorrow.
I see hope and courage in you.
It is not the sudden outbreak, the persistence along the journey that is matter.
Only the people who had been truly hardworking will understand the importance of talent.
